utation management.

By
the way, Judge Lewis Liman granted a motion by The New York Times today to =
pause discovery, pending a ruling on its motion to dismiss. He nodded to th=
e =E2=80=9Cdelicate and complicated issues=E2=80=9D raised by seeking docum=
ents and depositions from a journalistic outfit. Next up is the protective =
