urprisingly, Paramount=E2=80=99s special committee=E2=80=94formed to evalua=
te bids=E2=80=94rejected it outright.

But that rejection didn=E2=80=99t sit well with a handful of New York pensi=
on funds, which hold stakes in Paramount, and they=E2=80=99re taking the fi=
ght to the Delaware Court of Chancery. The pension funds, perhaps eyeing a =
