In a sealed briefing, Paramount=E2=80=99s special committee has apparently =
warned that granting the restraining order could trigger Skydance=E2=80=99s=
 right to walk away from the deal. Given how aggressively Ellison pursued R=
edstone=E2=80=99s position, there=E2=80=99s no reason to believe he=E2=80=
=99d actually pull out=E2=80=94but the fact that
